                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If He were living -- dare I ask --</l>
                    <l>And how if He be dead --</l>
                    <l>And so around the Words I went --</l>
                    <l>Of meeting them -- afraid --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I hinted Changes -- Lapse of Time --</l>
                    <l>The Surfaces of Years --</l>
                    <l>I touched with Caution -- lest they <app type="revision"><lem>slit --</lem><rdg>slit --</rdg></app>
crack --</l>
                    <l>And show me to my fears --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Reverted to adjoining Lives --</l>
                    <l>Adroitly turning out</l>
                    <l>Wherever I suspected Graves --</l>
                    <l>'Twas prudenter -- I thought --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And He -- I pushed -- with sudden force --</l>
                    <l>In face of the Suspense --</l>
                    <l>"Was buried" -- "Buried"! "He!"</l>
                    <l>My Life just holds the Trench --</l>
                </lg>
